<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="dying-adj">dying <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'daɪɪŋ/    美 /'daɪɪŋ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>垂死的；临终的；快熄灭的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>sb’s <strong>dying wish</strong>
某人的临终心愿</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A man should study till his <strong>dying day</strong>.
活到老，学到老。</p></div></div>